overview.en: CPOS is the token issued by CoinPOS, used for the ecological circulation, which includes mobile payment of physical goods, cryptocurrency exchange, or security service fees generated on the CPOS platform, etc.
overview.zh: CPOS是整个CoinPOS生态中具有价值并可流通的交互媒介，可用于移动支付购买实体货物、兑换虚拟货币，或支付CPOS平台包括券商服务所产生的费用。
